1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:20,000
New session — it already remembers what you told it last time.
No full history resent.

2
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Chatbots don't have memory — they have a context window.
It fills, they forget, or you resend everything.

3
00:00:45,000 --> 00:01:25,000
The engine lets memory settle —
form, decay, merge, crystallize into a self.

4
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:55,000
Each turn the model sees only a small, relevant working set —
not the whole log.

5
00:01:55,000 --> 00:02:20,000
Measured vs a full-history baseline — one critical fact out of 31
at a fraction of the tokens. Reported honestly, including what's not solved yet.

6
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:40,000
And เชียงใหม่ senses the real world — live weather and air —
a living proof, not just a demo.

7
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:56,000
All inference runs on Qwen Cloud / Alibaba Cloud Model Studio.
Open source, Apache-2.0. — Living Memory Engine
